<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-23-0529 </DOCNO><TEXT>The paper reviews the broader issues that affect nuclear power in a worldenergy context. The importance of nuclear power as an energy source isdescribed, as well as the environmental effects of different energy sources.The risks associated with the nuclear industry are discussed with respectto: risks due to radiation exposure, risks to workers in the nuclearindustry, and risks to the public due to discharges from nuclear installations.(U.K.).</TEXT></DOC>